{"tid":1183832,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做毒撚得罪你地？","createTime":"2019-06-03T08:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T15:30:50.000Z","uid":71508,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"56af01924bde1468b3cb1ce98da653dcfc9e9dee","tid":1183832,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"首先 係連登講做毒撚預左比大家負皮。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係鼓吹備毒撚呢種風氣 只不過想就啱啱做野時受到不禮貌對待有感而發開個po。<br />\n<br />\n話說我做毒撚需要進出商廈住宅，<br />\n平時入住宅做野需要保安開門然後登記。<br />\n<br />\n咁啱啱保安去左廁所，然後我就諗住等人開門入去涼下冷氣等佢返黎啦。<br />\n然後個有個住客開左門》對眼掃瞄哂我全身〉望到我著住件動漫T,拎住個finger 即刻轉左個勁鄙視既眼神望住我，講左句：你邊位呀？<br />\n我就回應：我係xxxx....<br />\nFeel到佢真係當我做賊咁，最後個保安返左黎就沒然後了。<br />\n<br />\n我平時冇著動漫T都遇過呢種問題。<br />\n但今日洗完，加上天氣太濕熱就著咗，公司無指引話唔俾著/要著動漫T，亦知道我有唔著普通T-shirt 方便開工嘅習慣。<br />\n<br />\n我想講做毒撚唔等於壞人，我唔會講d咩去美化/合理化成件事，只係想大家比小小尊重，我只不過係一個普通打工仔。"},{"pid":"991ffc437de3fcfac13a1242c9b4f908892ed51b","tid":1183832,"uid":175598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2224b522370af63558044989e9e7369fa40bf743","tid":1183832,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"991ffc437de3fcfac13a1242c9b4f908892ed51b","tid":1183832,"uid":175598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"Is"},{"pid":"daa56a084ffb2cfb739b618cfb6b457dc72ed9e1","tid":1183832,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c56c6ca1264bae756725b6819d4d75df025303","tid":1183832,"uid":136038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"我有十隻fingers"},{"pid":"b55198ae0ea827a33a948823182c856fefc58964","tid":1183832,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"樓主 我都係毒撚 但係我算人見人愛嗰隻<br />\n同埋都試過俾女溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔怕老實講 全部都係豬扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc89c644df7a885cf587e43657c89b305df19f07","tid":1183832,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"毒撚就收皮啦"}]}